{"id":435830,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/04/【图说天朝】洛阳豪华钉子户/","date":"2016-04-25T08:00:05Z","modified":"2016-04-25T08:00:05Z","title":"【图说天朝】洛阳豪华钉子户","content":"<p>2016年4月23日，在河南省洛阳市西工区某大型城中村拆迁现场，一幢五层的小洋楼格外引人注目，该小洋楼顶部不但设有两层观光亭台，并且外表华丽对称结构。该小洋楼周边已陆续拆迁完毕，并且不远处已开始进入地基施工。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-435831\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083666205.jpg\" alt=\"W020160425342083666205\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083666205.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083666205-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083666205-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-435832\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083904928.jpg\" alt=\"W020160425342083904928\" width=\"600\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083904928.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083904928-300x193.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342083904928-768x495.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>据现场施工人员介绍，该房屋主人为这个改造的城中村的村支部书记，因所住房屋为五层洋房成本高，可能因一直不满意政府及开发商等拆迁赔款及安置问题，因此无人敢去轻易拆迁，因此一直搁浅等待解决。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-435834\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084215093.jpg\" alt=\"W020160425342084215093\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084215093.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084215093-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084215093-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-435833\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084067301.jpg\" alt=\"W020160425342084067301\" width=\"600\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084067301.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084067301-300x180.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084067301-768x460.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/W020160425342084067301-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[30899,24930,23731]}